## Objective
Verify network connectivity using common Windows networking commands.

## Environment
- Windows 11
- VirtualBox
- Command Prompt
- PowerShell

## Commands Used
- ipconfig
- ping
- tracert

## Skills Demonstrated
- TCP/IP
- Network Troubleshooting
- Connectivity Testing
- Gateway Verification

## Procedure
1. Displayed IP configuration using ipconfig.
2. Verified local network connectivity.
3. Tested remote connectivity with ping.
4. Used tracert to identify the network path.
5. Documented results.

## Outcome
Successfully verified network connectivity and demonstrated basic troubleshooting techniques.

